prompt:
Please provide an example of a time when you had to make a decision using data analysis skills at work.
In my previous role as a marketing analyst, I was tasked with reviewing our company's social media analytics data. The objective was to identify trends and opportunities for growth. After thoroughly examining the metrics, I noticed that one of our posts on Instagram received significantly higher engagement compared to other platforms. This discovery led me to decide that we should invest more resources in creating content optimized for Instagram. As a result, we saw an increase in followers and overall brand awareness.
